{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state and progress of an inactive or completed pack are computed lazily. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you need the state or progress of a pack whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" property is currently"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set to "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", observe KVO change notifications on this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path, then call this method. Alternatively, you can add an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"observer for "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" about this pack that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"come from the default notification center."}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"requestProgress","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"requestProgress"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)requestProgress","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}],"title":"MLNOfflinePack","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/requestProgress":{"title":"requestProgress","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"requestProgress"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documenta